## Spacing System

### Base Unit: 4px
Use multiples of 4px for all spacing to maintain consistent rhythm.

### Spacing Scale
- **XXS**: 4px - Icon to text, tight groupings
- **XS**: 8px - Button padding (vertical), compact spacing
- **SM**: 12px - Form field gaps, list item spacing
- **MD**: 16px - Standard element spacing, card padding (small)
- **LG**: 24px - Section spacing (small), component gaps
- **XL**: 32px - Card padding, modal padding
- **2XL**: 48px - Section spacing (medium), content blocks
- **3XL**: 64px - Major section spacing, page margins
- **4XL**: 96px - Hero spacing, dramatic section breaks
- **5XL**: 128px - Maximum spacing, landing page sections

### Spacing Guidelines
- **Paragraph spacing**: 24px between paragraphs
- **Section spacing**: Minimum 64px between major sections
- **Card internal padding**: 32px-48px for breathing room
- **Container max-width**: 1280px-1440px for optimal readability
- **Side margins**: Minimum 24px mobile, 48px-96px desktop

