## Micro-interactions

### Animations
- Page transitions: 300ms ease-in-out
- Hover effects: 200ms ease
- Modal appearances: 250ms ease-out with slight scale
- Scrolling: Smooth scroll behavior enabled

### Feedback
- Success: Brief green checkmark (appears and fades)
- Error: Subtle red border pulse
- Added to cart: Smooth fly-to-cart animation

