## Design Don'ts

❌ **Avoid:**
- Cluttered layouts with insufficient spacing
- Multiple competing CTAs in the same section
- Heavy shadows or gradients (keep it flat and clean)
- Too many colors (stick to white + red + grays)
- Complex animations that distract from content
- Small touch targets on mobile
- Long paragraphs without breaks
- Underlined text except for links

✓ **Instead:**
- Embrace whitespace generously
- One primary CTA per section
- Subtle elevation through minimal shadows
- Disciplined color palette
- Purposeful micro-interactions
- Minimum 44px touch targets
- Short paragraphs, scannable content
- Clear link styling with color/weight changes